        "Certificate of Undergraduate Study in Cosmetic Science": [
            "Certificate of Undergraduate Study in Cosmetic Science The Certificate in Undergraduate Study in Cosmetic Science will provide students with specialized study to enhance knowledge and skills necessary for employment in the cosmetic industry. Students learn how to appropriately use raw materials to make new products and then develop, formulate, and assess the safety and quality of the products for human use. They study regulations and how to assess productsâ€™ safety, performance and quality to ensure that they understand how safe, effective, and environmentally friendly products are scientifically formulated."
